divs: Sighting DetailsTHIS JUST HAPPENED AGAIN . BUT THIS TIME THERE IS A THIRD WITNESS TOGETHER THOUGH A YEAR AGO MY HUSBAND AND I SAW THE SAME THING GOING NORTH TOWARD THE LAKE. TONIGHT THE THREE OF US SA 2 LIGHTS GOING SOUTH. BUT MY HUSBAND SAID HE SAW A THIRD LIGHT. WHAT WE SAW WERE 2 LIGHTS PERFECTLY IN DIMENSION GOING SIDE BY SIDE. FIRST MY HUSBAND SAW THE LIGHTS THEN POINTED THEM OUT TO ME AND MY NEIGHBOR AND WE SAW WHAT WE SAW.THEY LOOKED AS IF THEY WERE JOY RIDING QUIETLY. BUT I HAVE A EXPERIENCE FROM 28 YEARS AGO DOCUMENTED WITH THE N.U.R.C. AND I AHVE HAD A FEW OTHER SIGHTINGS NOT DOCUMENTED,I JUST NEED TO SAY WHAT I SAW IN CASE ANYONE ELSE SAW IT TO.
